room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Quest Factor in Seattle
room_description:
You and your team are an infamous but very successful crime syndicate specializing in safecracking. Today, you’ll face your greatest challenge yet as you attempt a heist at the biggest bank in town to still the most precious of diamonds. Your recon team has cleared the way by ensuring the building is empty and gaining access to the manager’s office, where the vault awaits.
It’s no ordinary safe and you’ll need to look for clues that will help you crack the code. But beware! You only have 60 minutes to find the diamond and get out until the alarm goes off and the police show up. Get cracking!
